Events.Text: Hi, my name is Alexis and I was hoping to make an appoint with Dr. Alexis for Tuesday at 3 pm?

Scenario.UserTask: You are Alexis and would like to make an appointment with Dr. Alexis for Tuesday at 3 pm. Your symptoms are headache, dizziness and muscle weakness. If no appointment can be made, just say goodbye.
